  <!-- EN: Accompanied by chilling scratches and mournful cries from all around, mounds of desolate graves emerged near the colony. -->
  <RI_Exorcism_CursedGravesSpawn.letterText>伴随着四周传来的阵阵刺耳的刮擦声和凄厉的哭喊声，一片片荒凉的坟墓出现在了这个殖民地附近。</RI_Exorcism_CursedGravesSpawn.letterText>
  
