  <!-- EN: Several colonists were suddenly struck with a burning fever, their bodies growing frail — It is cursing.\n\nSeek a way to break the curse, or it will steadily worsen until it utterly consumes their lives. -->
  <RI_Exorcism_CurseSpread.letterText>几名殖民者突然发了高烧，变得虚弱，这正是诅咒作祟。\n\n寻找能解除诅咒的办法，否则诅咒将逐渐加深，直至彻底吞噬他们的性命。</RI_Exorcism_CurseSpread.letterText>
  
